## Game-owned shared assets

The initial scaffold contains no shared asset bytes. Before adding a file below
`game_data/shared/`, record its origin, copyright holder, license identifier,
source URL when applicable, and whether it was modified in this section. For an
original asset, identify the game copyright owner and distribution license.
`game_data/shared.lock.json` hashes this complete notices file so the reviewed
attribution and the shared runtime inventory travel together.
